      Before starting, load design.md §5.1, §5.2, INV-5, INV-7, spec.md FR-BF-01, FR-BF-04, NFR-04. Follow task-execute Step 0 (rigor declaration: FULL) before writing any code. Step 9.5 quality gates (code-review + adr-check) are mandatory at task completion.
